RENT AFFAIRS INFORMATION IN LOCAL GOVERNMENT.     PAPER PRESENTED AT THE ASLIB CONFERENCE, CURRENT AFFAIRS' INFORMATION ANDRESOURCES, LONDON, 4 JUNE 81. DISCUSSES THE SCOPE OF LOCAL GOVERNMENT IN THEUK, ITS RESPONSIBILITIES AND THE PRESSURES THAT IT CURRENTLY FACES. ALSOCONSIDERS THE TYPES OF CURRENT AFFAIRS INFORMATION THAT LOCAL GOVERNMENT NEEDSAND HOW THIS INFORMATION IS COORDINATED. DESCRIBES HOW DEVON AND CHESHIRECOUNTY COUNCILS AND THE GREATER LONDON COUNCIL HAVE TACKLED THE PROBLEMS OFCOORDINATION